Summary: 
 * Fixed ACJF_ARG_DEBUG macro
 * Modified ACJF_CHECK_CROSSTOOL to not change CFLAGS or CXXFLAGS
   - ACJF_CHECK_CROSSTOOL( CC, gcc)  auto added "-g -O2" to CFLAGS
   - ACJF_CHECK_CROSSTOOL( CXX, g++) auto added "-g -O2" to CXXFLAGS
   - AC_PROG_CC / AC_PROG_CXX still does auto add "-g -O2" if compiler
     supports it and CFLAGS / CXXFLAGS where not set previously
